"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/807229","Home Office","false","2017-12-21","<p>The Scottish Government has decided that it does not wish section 50 of the Crime and Courts Act 2013 to be commenced in full in Scotland and there is no timetable for its commencement. This is a decision for the Scottish Government and there have been no recent discussions on the issue.</p>","Great Yarmouth","Brandon Lewis","119876 ; 119877","2017-12-21T17:12:21.583Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/807229/answer","Biography information for Brandon Lewis","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/807229/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/807229/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2017-12-15","Extradition: Scotland","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, for what reasons section 50 of the Crime and Courts Act 2013 has not been commenced in Scotland.","false","Biography information for Mr Alistair Carmichael","Orkney and Shetland","Mr Alistair Carmichael","119875"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/807230","Home Office","false","2017-12-21","<p>The Scottish Government has decided that it does not wish section 50 of the Crime and Courts Act 2013 to be commenced in full in Scotland and there is no timetable for its commencement. This is a decision for the Scottish Government and there have been no recent discussions on the issue.</p>","Great Yarmouth","Brandon Lewis","119875 ; 119877","2017-12-21T17:12:21.647Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/807230/answer","Biography information for Brandon Lewis","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/807230/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/807230/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2017-12-15","Extradition: Scotland","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what the timetable is for the commencement of section 50 of the Crime and Courts Act 2013 in Scotland.","false","Biography information for Mr Alistair Carmichael","Orkney and Shetland","Mr Alistair Carmichael","119876"
